spec_data.Name: glite-lbjp-common-gsoap-plugin
spec_data.Description:
glite-security-gsoap-plugin is plugin for gSoap providing secured communication
via GSS, as well as strict timing control of all operations via
glite-security-gss.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Thu 03 Aug 2017 04:29:36 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Plugin for gSoap to use glite-security-gss as the communication layer
